Foundation?s assessment of prospective candidates.  


REQUIREMENTS
Eligibility Criteria
The Foundation will award its PG scholarship to students who fulfil the following criteria:

 

Indian nationals residing in India at the time of application as it is mandatory for shortlisted 
candidates to attend a face to face interview
Students below 30 years of age.
Graduates of a recognised university (students in the final year of a degree course and those 
awaiting their results are also eligible to apply).
Students having sought admission for a postgraduate degree programme at any prestigious university
 for the fall intake(Those who are awaiting a decision from a university are also eligible to apply.
 However, the award of the scholarship is subject to them securing admission).
