Application Process
Step 1: The mode of application for the Foundation?s postgraduate scholarships is online: The 
candidate is required to complete the registration online at http://pg.nsfoundation.co.in.

Step 2: Upon registration for the Foundation?s PG Scholarship, the login credentials will be sent
 to the registered email ID. Once the registration is
